  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This adversarial package intentionally omits acceptanceCriteria fields on several credibility factors to trigger W-AR-01 (missing acceptance criteria). Decision is recorded as Accepted despite factors falling below required levels, reflecting the targeted weakness.",
