    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels. Six factors were not assessed due to epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Despite the shortfalls, the team accepted the model for the stated COU on the basis of compensating engineering judgment and the availability of Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification results. Note: multiple factors lack documented acceptanceCriteria rationale, representing a gap in the formal credibility evidence package.",
